            </div>
            <div class="slide-body">
                <div class="col-text">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Inheriting a Monolith:</strong> Inherited a massive, highly regulated application suite with deep usability debt in workflow configuration.</li>
                        <li><strong>The Precedent Model:</strong> Defining what tasks came <em>before</em> forced users to think backward, making conditional logic configuration highly error-prone.</li>
                        <li><strong>Usability Testing:</strong> Evaluated in a usability study one sprint before implementation, where **100% of participants** struggled with the precedents model and failed conditional configuration.</li>
                        <li><strong>Redesigned Dependent Grid:</strong> Overhauling to a **Dependent model** with cell-specific validations reduced cognitive load, while flowchart requests established the business case for CMS.</li>
                    </ul>
